title: Lafangey - Sapne, Dosti, Duniya
overview: The season begins with Chatty, Rohan and Kammo trying to figure out what to do next. It's been a while since they graduated; the family has started to taunt them, their romantic relationships are at stake, and life just seems to pass them by without answers. The people are not delusional; they are hardworking and dedicated, but it's just the state of the country where there are no jobs.
